FROM LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRD41664410031195_shipper_rate_date_extended AS shipper_rate_date_extended
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV4TI1664410049053_budget_product_daily AS budget_product_daily ON (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(budget_product_daily.actual_date ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) = (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ), 'YYYY-MM-DD'))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV2F51664410088272_shipments_actual AS shipments_actual ON shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey and
      shipments_actual.shipper_application_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_APPLICATION_ID") and
      shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."TRANSFIX_LANE_ID") and
      shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer = (shipper_rate_date_extended."IS_DROP_TRAILER")
WHERE ((( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) >= ((DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND ( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) < ((DATEADD('month', 1, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ))
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
